    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> coated</strong> <strong>basa pieces </strong>to the pan and cook for an initial 3-4 min</p><p>After 3-4 min, turn the basa, add the <strong>remaining herb marinade</strong> to the pan and cook for a further 3-4 min or until the basa is cooked through - this is your <strong>lemony basa</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
